title: Obersee Rio Diaper Bag Backpack
transcripts:
The Obersee Rio Diaper Bag Backpack With Detachable Cooler is the perfect solution for moms and dads on the go who would like to have their hands free, but still be able to tote all of the baby essentials.  

The backpack features a detachable insulated bottle cooler that is perfect size for up to three bottles or for snacks. The cooler easily detaches from the backpack and features an exterior pocket, carry handle with clip for easy attachment to a stroller, and adjustable straps for easy carrying or attaching the cooler by itself to a stroller.  Additional coolers, available in many colors, may be purchased separately.  The backpack includes four straps for easily attaching the cooler, and these straps may be easily hidden into small openings on the backpack when not in use.  

The backpack includes a padded changing mat that folds compactly to fit into the backpack for changes on the go. The mat is padded to protect babies from rough surfaces and features a large, easy to clean changing surface.  

The backpack features a large main compartment with a large pocket that is perfect for holding the changing mat, or a computer, as well as 3 small and large mesh pockets for holding diapers, wipes, pacifiers, and other changing supplies. 

The front section of the Rio backpack contains a large mesh zipper pocket intended for keeping clothing and blankets neatly stowed. The mesh allows you to easily view the contents. The front section also includes a key clip and a zipper pocket for keeping personal items such as keys and mobile phones.  

The front of the backpack also features a zipper pocket for easy to access storage  or the perfect spot for placing, and easily accessing, wet wipes.  

The exterior of the backpack has two side drink pockets for drinks or baby bottles. For added comfort, the back has comfortable padding and the straps are lined with breathable mesh padding. The top features a carry handle and two rings for easy attachment to stroller (stroller straps sold separately).

The Rio diaper backpack is a great solution for parents on the go with many practical qualities. Get yours today!
